frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature figures working on a dessert landscape, adorned with lemon slices and powdered sugar. The figures are engaged in various activities, such as climbing ladders and carrying baskets filled with lemon pieces. The vibrant yellow of the lemons contrasts with the white sugar, creating a playful and imaginative atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene is a creative and playful depiction of tiny figures interacting with a dessert landscape. The setting is reminiscent of a lemon tart, with the figures appearing to be harvesting and arranging lemon slices and powdered sugar.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature figures working on a lemon tart, with tiny workers climbing ladders and carrying baskets of lemon slices. frames.description: The scene is a creative and imaginative representation of tiny figures engaged in the task of 'harvesting' lemon slices from a tart. The setting is a close-up view of a dessert, with a focus on the interaction between the miniature workers and the food elements.
